OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally dry day with some
OL,6,Fsunshine at times, but cloud bubbling
OL,7,Fup through the afternoon. Isolated
OL,8,Fshowers may break out in the east, but
OL,9,Fmost places will stay dry. Feeling
OL,10,Fcooler than of late in the light
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells overnight with
OL,14,Fpatchy cloud. Isolated shower towards
OL,15,Fthe west but staying mostly dry.
OL,16,FFrosty patches under clear spells,
OL,17,Fmostly in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
