OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry start to the
OL,6,Fday but more cloud developing through
OL,7,Fthe morning which will develop into
OL,8,Ffurther showers into the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAfter
OL,11,Fchilly start, Friday will be dry for
OL,12,Fmany, but showers are possible, these
OL,13,Flocally heavy on Friday. Longer
OL,14,Fperiods of rain are possible on
OL,15,FSaturday and Sunday. Turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
